Class Date

java.lang.Object
payroll.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Date>
public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Date>
This class defines the Date object. The Date object is defaulted to the current date unless specified.
Author:
KJ Wang, Mehdi Kamal
